        <title>《世界上最简单的会计书》读书笔记</title>
        <link>https://blog.nav8.top/p/%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%80%E7%AE%80%E5%8D%95%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E8%AE%A1%E4%B9%A6%E8%AF%BB%E4%B9%A6%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</link>
